		<dl class="linksItem friendlink" id="newcar">
			<h2><dt class="b-left">二手车热门搜索</dt></h2>

        })();

		success : function(results) {
			var parsedJson = jQuery.parseJSON(results);
			if (parsedJson.code === 0 && parsedJson.data != null) {
				var captcha = ISDCaptcha({
					'element' : 'ISDCaptcha',
					'width' :parsedJson.data.width ,//宽度
					'type' : parsedJson.data.level,//验证码级别
					'showType'   : 'win', //  ['embed', 'trigger', 'win']//如果不传此值，默认为嵌入式.embed：嵌入式.trigger：触发式.win:弹出式
					'sessionId' : parsedJson.data.sessionId,
					'targetElm':'btnSubmit',//只对弹出式有效,如果是根据后端策略确定是否为弹出时
					//'winAutoShow':true,//弹出式时添加此属性会自动弹出,默认为false,不自动弹出
					'successCallback' : function successCallback(data) {

						respMessage = $.ajax({
							url : "checkcode.do",
							data : {
								namespace : namespace,
								sessionId : parsedJson.data.sessionId,
								url : url,
								successToken : data.successToken,
								uuid:uuid,
								serialId:serialId
							},
							type : "POST",
							async : true,
							success : function(results) {
								var parsedJson = jQuery.parseJSON(results);
								if (parsedJson.code === 0) {
									var redLocation = parsedJson.msg;
									if(redLocation.indexOf("http://")==-1 && redLocation.indexOf("https://")==-1){
										redLocation = "http://"+redLocation;
									}
									window.location.href = redLocation;
								} else {
									$("#errmsg").html(parsedJson.msg);
									
								}
							}
						});
					},
					'failCallback' : function failCallback(data) {
						//alert(data.responseId);
					}
				})
				captcha.init();
			} else {
				$("#errmsg").html(parsedJson.msg);
				
			}
		}
	});
	
	function pv () {  
	    var params = {};  
	    //Document对象数据  
	    if(document) {  
	        params.domain = document.domain || '';   
	        params.url = document.URL || '';   
	        params.title = document.title || '';   
	        params.referrer = document.referrer || '';   
	    }     
	    //Window对象数据  
	    if(window && window.screen) {  
	        params.sh = window.screen.height || 0;  
	        params.sw = window.screen.width || 0;  
	        params.cd = window.screen.colorDepth || 0;  
	    }     
	    //navigator对象数据  
	    if(navigator) {  
	        params.lang = navigator.language || '';   
	    }     
	   
	    // 其他参数  
	    var date = new Date();  
	    params.ltime = date.getTime() / 1000;  
	    //拼接参数串  
	    var args = '';   
	    for(var i in params) {  
	        if(args != '') {  
	            args += '&';  
	        }     
	        args += i + '=' + encodeURIComponent(params[i]);  
	    }     
	   
	    //通过Image对象请求后端脚本  
	    var img = new Image(1, 1);   
	    img.src = '/fwdata/load.gif?' + args;  
	}
});

</script>
</html>

<script type="text/javascript">
 $.fn.lazyload=(function(){
        var doc_element=document.compatMode == 'BackCompat' ? document.body : document.documentElement;
        var defaults={
            lazyAttr:'lazy_src',//保存SRC的自定义属性
            upBuffer:200,//向上缓冲的距离
            downBuffer:300,//向下缓冲的距离
            bufferTime:100,//滚动时缓冲的时间
            defultSrc:"//j2.58cdn.com.cn/n/images/list/noimg.gif"//初始化时的默认图片
        };
        function lazyload(sel,options){
            var that=this;
            this.opt=$.extend(defaults, options);
            this.elList=[];
            this.lazyList=[];
            this.sel=sel;
            $(function(){
                that.el=$(that.sel).filter('['+that.opt.lazyAttr+']');
                that.el.each(function(i){
                    that.opt.defultSrc&&$(this).attr('src',that.opt.defultSrc);
                    var lazySrc=$(this).attr(that.opt.lazyAttr);
                    lazySrc&&that.elList.push({el:this,
                        src:lazySrc});
                });
                $(that.elList).each(function(i){this.i=i;})
                that.num=that.elList.length;
                that.loadEl();
                that.bindEvent();
            });
       }
        lazyload.fn=lazyload.prototype;
        lazyload.fn.bindEvent=function(){
            var that=this;
            $(window).bind('resize',function(){
                that.lazyLoadEl();
            });
            $(window).bind('scroll',function(){
                that.lazyLoadEl();
            });
        };
        lazyload.fn.getlazyList= function (){
            var that=this,offset=$(document).scrollTop(),before_offset=offset-that.opt.upBuffer,
            visio_offset = offset + doc_element.clientHeight+that.opt.downBuffer;
            that.lazyList= $.grep(that.elList,function(item){
                item.top=item.top||getTop(item.el);
                return !item.loaded&&item.top<visio_offset&&item.top>before_offset;
            });
            return that.lazyList;
        };
        lazyload.fn.lazyLoadEl= function (){
            var that=this;
            clearTimeout(that.gt);
            that.gt=setTimeout(function(){
                that.loadEl();
            },that.opt.bufferTime);
        };
        lazyload.fn.loadEl=function (){
            var that=this;
            if(this.num<1||this.getlazyList().length<1){
                clearTimeout(this.gt);
                return;
            }
            $(this.lazyList).each(function(){
                $(this.el).attr('src',this.src);
                that.elList[this.i].loaded=true;
                that.num--;
            });
        };
        function getTop(el){
            if (!el) return null;
            var element=el,offsetTop = element.offsetTop;
            while (element = element.offsetParent) {
                offsetTop += element.offsetTop;
            }
            return offsetTop;
        }
        return function(options){
            new lazyload(this.selector,options);
            return this;
        };
    })();
var DispCateID = $("#DispCateID").val();
 $.ajax({
    url:'//hezuo.58.com/investment/web/catepage/',
	data: 'cateid='+DispCateID+'', 
    dataType:"jsonp",  
    jsonpCallback:"getInfoJson",
    success:function(data){
        for(var obj in data){
            if(0 == data[obj].length) continue;
            var html = '<div class="hezuo clearfix"><ul>';  
            var myUrl = "";
           
            for(var i=0,len = data[obj].length; i<len; i++) {
                myUrl = "//jing.58.com/adJump?target="+data[obj][i].target+"&from="+window.location.href.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g, "&quot;").replace(/'/g, "&#39;")+"&pc=1&cateid="+DispCateID+"&cooperator="+data[obj][i].cooperator+"&position=6";
                html += '<li><a href="'+myUrl+'" target="_blank"><img src="//j2.58cdn.com.cn/n/images/list/noimg.gif" lazy_src='+data[obj][i].pic+' width="100" height="75"><p><span>'+data[obj][i].title+'</span></p>'+decodeURI(decodeURI(data[obj][i].touzhijine))+'</a></li>';
            }
            html += '</ul></div>';
            $('#key_'+DispCateID).append(html);
        }
        $('img').lazyload();
    }
}); 
</script>

    <link href="/js/jquery-ui-1.11.4.custom/jquery-ui.min.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script type="text/javascript">
        //授权代理商查询
        function query1() {
            //统计代码
            biz_agent_search_click();

            var agentBusinessName = $("#queryForm1 #agentBusinessName").val();

            if ($.trim(agentBusinessName) == "") {
                alert("请输入代理商企业名称进行查询");
                return false;
            }

            $.ajax({
                type : "POST",
                data : {"agentBusinessName" : agentBusinessName},
                url	:  "/agent/searchagent",
                async : true,
                success : function(data){
                    try{
                        var agent = JSON.parse(data);
                        $("#warning").text(agent.warning);
                        $("#noResult").dialog({
                            title: '授权代理商查询',
                            width: 750,
                            height: 300,
                            closed: false,
                            cache: false,
                            modal: true
                        });
                        //统计代码
                        biz_agent_searchstate_load("A");
                    }catch(e) {
                        $("#hasResult").html(data).dialog({
                            title: '授权代理商查询',
                            width: 750,
                            height: 400,
                            closed: false,
                            cache: false,
                            modal: true
                        });
                        //统计代码
                        biz_agent_searchstate_load("B");
                    }
                }
            });

            return false;
        }

        //按照城市查询城市负责人
        function query2 () {

            var cityId = $("#queryForm2 #cityId").val();
            if ("0" == cityId) {
                alert("请选择查询城市");
                return;
            }
            var cityName = $("#queryForm2 #cityId option[value="+cityId+"]").text();
            cityName = cityName.substring(1);
            //统计代码
            biz_agent_tel_search_click($("#cityId").val());

            $.ajax({
                type : "POST",
                data : {"cityId" : cityId},
                url	:  "/agent/searchmanager",
                async : true,
                success : function(data){
                    $("#city").html(cityName);
                    var managers = JSON.parse(data);
                    var table =$("<table>");
                    var currentTr;
                    var len = managers.length;
                    if(len==0){
                        $("#tt").html("<tr><td><p>黄页招聘招商电话: 400-818-1858</p><p>房产招商电话：400-810-7858</p></td></tr>");
                        $("#contactMe").dialog({
                            title: '区域招商负责人查询',
                            width: 750,
                            height: 270,
                            closed: false,
                            cache: false,
                            modal: true
                        });
                        return;
                    }

                    for(var i=0 ; i<len;i++){
                        var manager = managers[i];
                        if(manager.managerRealName){
                            if(i%2==0){
                                currentTr =$("<tr>");
                                table.append(currentTr);
                            }
                            var td = $("<td>");
                            currentTr.append(td);

                            var p2 = $("<p>");
                            p2.html('<b>城市经理：</b><span id="manager">'+manager.managerRealName+'</span>(负责'+manager.productLineName+')');
                            td.append(p2);

                            var p3 = $("<p>");
                            p3.html('<b>联系方式：</b><span id="mobile">'+manager.mobile+'</span>');
                            td.append(p3);

                            var p4 = $("<p>");
                            p4.html('<b>电子邮箱：</b><span id="email">'+manager.email+'</span>');
                            td.append(p4);
                        }

                    }
                    $("#tt").html(table.html());
                    $("#contactMe").dialog({
                        title: '区域招商负责人查询',
                        width: 750,
                        height: 270,
                        closed: false,
                        cache: false,
                        modal: true
                    });

                }
            });

        }

        //申请代理
        function query3(){
            biz_applyform_load();
            location.href="/agent/toapply";
        }

        /**************以下是统计代码部分*********************/

        //申请代理页面加载统计
        function biz_applyform_load()
        {
            _gaq.push(['pageTracker._trackEvent', 'biz', 'click', '/biz/applyform/load']);
            clickLog('from=biz_applyform_load');
        }

        //授权代理商“查询”按钮点击统计
        function biz_agent_search_click()
        {
            _gaq.push(['pageTracker._trackEvent', 'biz', 'click', '/biz/agent/search/click']);
            clickLog('from=biz_agent_search_click');
        }

        //授权代理商“查询”结果统计
        function biz_agent_searchstate_load(state)
        {
            _gaq.push(['pageTracker._trackEvent', 'biz', 'click', '/biz/agent/searchstate/load/' + state + '/']);
            clickLog('from=biz_agent_searchstate_load_' + state);
        }

        //授权代理商分城市查询统计
        function biz_agent_tel_search_click(city)
        {
            _gaq.push(['pageTracker._trackEvent', 'biz', 'click', '/biz/agent/tel/search/click/' + city + '/']);
            clickLog('from=biz_agent_tel_search_click_' + city)
        }
    </script>
